nodes.text: The Star Wars Archives: Episodes I–III, 1999–2005

The Star Wars Archives: Episodes I–III, 1999–2005 is a reference book based on the Star Wars prequel trilogy. It was written by Paul Duncan and published by TASCHEN on December 13, 2020. The book was preceded by The Star Wars Archives: Episodes IV–VI, 1977–1983 in 2018.
